### CRUD Operations Test Suite

### 1. CREATE - Add new medication
POST {{baseUrl}}/medicamentos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "id": "test-antibiotico-500mg",
  "name": "Test Antibiótico novissimo",
  "variation": "500 mg / 1 mL",
  "volumeMl": 1,
  "amountMg": 500,
  "mgPerKgDefault": 20,
  "description": "Medicamento de teste para CRUD operations",
  "indications": ["Teste", "Desenvolvimento"],
  "image": "/images/ampola.svg"
}

### 2. READ - Verify medication was created
GET {{baseUrl}}/medicamentos/test-antibiotico-500mg

### 3. READ - List all medications (should include test med)
GET {{baseUrl}}/medicamentos

### 4. UPDATE - Modify the test medication
PUT {{baseUrl}}/medicamentos/test-antibiotico-500mg
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "id": "test-antibiotico-500mg",
  "name": "Test Antibiótico ATUALIZADO",
  "variation": "500 mg / 2 mL",
  "volumeMl": 2,
  "amountMg": 500,
  "mgPerKgDefault": 25,
  "description": "Medicamento de teste - MODIFICADO",
  "indications": ["Teste", "Desenvolvimento", "Verificação"],
  "image": "/images/ampola.svg"
}

### 5. READ - Verify update
GET {{baseUrl}}/medicamentos/test-antibiotico-500mg

### 6. DELETE - Remove test medication
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/medicamentos/test-antibiotico-500mg
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 7. READ - Verify deletion (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/medicamentos/test-antibiotico-500mg

